---
title: Lemon-Pepper Double Pork Chops with Roasted Veggies and Savoury Pan Sauce
description: Winner, winner, pork chop dinner! The bright flavours of these lemon and garlic pork chops are balanced by herby rice and aromatic, oven-roasted veggies. A quick and delicious pan sauce ties it all together.
